The paper focuses on similarity search on complex data types, which is a common problem in database systems (cs.DB) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of Locality Sensitive Hashing schemes also suggests a connection to data structures (cs.DS). The paper also mentions experiments on image data (cs.CV) and the use of machine learning techniques (cs.LG) for similarity search.
